  "title": "CrossFadeSceneTransition",
  "description": "Continuous blend between the outgoing scene (frozen as a snapshot at session start) and the incoming scene (rendered live to a pooled texture), with no \"exit half\"/\"enter half\" seam — `placement: 'scene'`, `outgoingFrame: 'snapshot'`, `currentFrame: 'texture'`. A full `SceneTransition`, not phase-split (definition spec §3.9.2, §8).",
